<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="full" lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="images/favicon.png" type="image/png">
    <title>Juniors CTF</title>
  
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Open+Sans:300,300i,400,400i,600,600i,700,700i,800,800i&amp;subset=cyrillic" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/material.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/main.css">
  
    <!--<script type="text/javascript" src="js/info.js"></script>-->
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="mdl-layout mdl-js-layout mdl-layout--fixed-header has-drawer is-upgraded">

      <div class="jctf-header mdl-layout__header mdl-layout__header--waterfall">
        <div class="mdl-layout__header-row">
          <span class="jctf-title mdl-layout-title">
            <img class="jctf-logo-image" src="images/logo.png">
          </span>
          
          <div class="jctf-navigation-container">
            <nav class="jctf-navigation mdl-navigation">
              <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="scoreboard.html">Scoreboard</a>
              <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="tasks.html">Tasks</a>
              <a class="mdl-navigation__link is-active" href="#">News</a>
              <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="sponsors.html">Sponsors</a>
            </nav>
          </div>
          <div id="info"></div>
          <span class="jctf-mobile-title mdl-layout-title">
            <img class="jctf-logo-image" src="images/logo.png">
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="jctf-drawer mdl-layout__drawer">
        <span class="mdl-layout-title">
          <img class="jctf-logo-image" src="images/logo.png">
        </span>
        <nav class="mdl-navigation">
          <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="scoreboard.html">Scoreboard</a>
          <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="tasks.html">Tasks</a>
          <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="news.html">News</a>
          <a class="mdl-navigation__link" href="sponsors.html">Sponsors</a>
        </nav>
      </div>

      <main class="jctf-content mdl-layout__content">
        <div class="jctf-content__cards mdl-grid">
          <div class="jctf-content__simple-card mdl-cell mdl-cell--12-col mdl-grid">
            <div class="jctf-simple-card mdl-cell mdl-cell--12-col">
              <div class="jctf-simple-card__block">
                <h4>News and hints</h4>
                  News and hints are published in telegram channel: 
                  <a href="https://t.me/juniors_ctf" target="_blank">https://t.me/juniors_ctf</a>.
              </div>
              <div class="jctf-simple-card__block">
                <h4>Flag format</h4>
                In order to avoid cheating we accept only formalized flag format, not a regular expression flag.
                <br>
                In most cases the flag is an English string (may contain numbers and other symbols), if it is not defined in the task.
              </div>
              <div class="jctf-simple-card__block">
                <h4>Points for solving tasks</h4>
                <div class="mdl-grid mdl-grid--no-spacing">
                  <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col mdl-cell--8-col-tablet mdl-cell--middle" style="text-align: justify">
                    At the start the cost of each task is 500 points.
                    While the number of solutions is growing, tasks are being re-evaluated.
                    The more teams have solved the task, the “cheaper” it gets. 
                    The minimum points you can get for solving one task is 100. <br>
                    After your team has sent us a flag, you get the number of points in which the task is evaluated at the moment.
                    If after that the cost for the task falls, <b>the points of each team are re-evaluated</b>.
                    Because of that the number of points may change.
                  </div>
                  <div class="mdl-cell mdl-cell--6-col mdl-cell--8-col-tablet mdl-cell--middle">
                    <img src="images/score_linear_formula.png" style="max-width: 100%">
                  </div>
                  <div class="jctf-simple-card__block">
                    <h4>Task status</h4>
                    <img src="images/closed_task.png" style="padding-right: 7px; width: 25px;">– closed.
                    <br>
                    <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #494747">500 </span>– the task is opened, nobody has solved it.
                    <br>
                    <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #0db4ca">500 </span>– the task is opened, one or more teams have solved it.
                    <br>
                    <span style="font-weight: 600; color: #46c529">500 </span>– your team has solved the task.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </main>
    </div>
    <script src="js/material.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
